snippet.title: STORY OF SEASONS: Pioneers of Olive Town - Gameplay Trailer - Begin Your New Life!
snippet.description:
Escape the hustle and bustle of the city and begin your new life in Olive Town! Follow one player’s journey as she breathes life into her grandfather’s old farm, repairing buildings, planting seeds, discovering new animal friends and enjoying everything life has to offer in her new hometown! What will be your STORY OF SEASONS?

STORY OF SEASONS: Pioneers of Olive Town is coming to Nintendo Switch in Europe and Australia on 26 March 2021!
